* MegaDrive = @{"os4depot.net/?function=showfile&file=emulation/gamesystem/dgen.lha" system "OpenURL URL \"http://os4depot.net/?function=showfile&file=emulation/gamesystem/dgen.lha\""}
* NeoGeo    = @{"os4depot.net/?function=showfile&file=emulation/gamesystem/gngeong.lha" system "OpenURL URL \"http://os4depot.net/?function=showfile&file=emulation/gamesystem/gngeong.lha\""}
* C64       = @{"os4depot.net/?function=showfile&file=emulation/computer/vice.tar.gz" system "OpenURL URL \"http://os4depot.net/?function=showfile&file=emulation/computer/vice.tar.gz\""}
* Spectrum  = @{"os4depot.net/?function=showfile&file=emulation/computer/fuse.lha" system "OpenURL URL \"http://os4depot.net/?function=showfile&file=emulation/computer/fuse.lha\""} (although the 68k "ASp" is arguably better)
